    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115030/extras/f99ecbeb75f0c6dddede4fd55179076e.poster.avif?t=1771085065\" width=800 height=166 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115030/extras/f99ecbeb75f0c6dddede4fd55179076e.webm?t=1771085065\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115030/extras/f99ecbeb75f0c6dddede4fd55179076e.mp4?t=1771085065\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong></strong><br><br><br><br><br><strong>CUBO</strong>将魔方经典玩法与剧情驱动的冒险解谜世界巧妙融合。探索精心打造的奇幻场景，解锁全新区域，在穿越破碎世界的旅程中邂逅神秘生物。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115030/extras/bb7c74cdbf218724c2c6b043c877d9e7.avif?t=1771085065\" width=1370 height=129 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115030/extras/6d7db608c6bf0b7d25e6972bf400b289.poster.avif?t=1771085065\" width=796 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115030/extras/6d7db608c6bf0b7d25e6972bf400b289.webm?t=1771085065\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115030/extras/6d7db608c6bf0b7d25e6972bf400b289.mp4?t=1771085065\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索立方体世界的隐秘角落，每个区域都拥有独特的生物群系，充满挑战与秘密。穿越地表世界，深入立方体内部，发掘全新区域。掌握新能力与机制，让你能够穿越曾经无法抵达的地块，开辟全新路径。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115030/extras/9a4a4bb08b936768c0e9c6510ad3c4c9.avif?t=1771085065\" width=1370 height=129 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115030/extras/47a555c98e577ee5c88b5f37478b2406.poster.avif?t=1771085065\" width=800 height=294 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115030/extras/47a555c98e577ee5c88b5f37478b2406.webm?t=1771085065\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115030/extras/47a555c98e577ee5c88b5f37478b2406.mp4?t=1771085065\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过解锁新地砖和立方体面推进游戏进程，逐步揭示世界的全貌。运用并组合先前发现的地砖来解开谜题、推进游戏进程，奖励富有创造性的探索。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115030/extras/cf28a1791c46f4ab61a9696b59f0a2b7.avif?t=1771085065\" width=1370 height=129 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115030/extras/2ee6ebf520b9cc370193f293d1091130.poster.avif?t=1771085065\" width=800 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115030/extras/2ee6ebf520b9cc370193f293d1091130.webm?t=1771085065\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115030/extras/2ee6ebf520b9cc370193f293d1091130.mp4?t=1771085065\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >揭开一个因自然失衡而支离破碎的世界的故事。作为立方行者，你的使命是修复那些破碎的片段。通过解开与环境结构紧密相连的谜题，拼凑出世界支离破碎的历史，让自然重归和谐。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115030/extras/462d1da9d1436df922df4ca780dc74f1.avif?t=1771085065\" width=1370 height=129 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115030/extras/051f6f101be5440e70fefded10d10dc2.poster.avif?t=1771085065\" width=800 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115030/extras/051f6f101be5440e70fefded10d10dc2.webm?t=1771085065\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115030/extras/051f6f101be5440e70fefded10d10dc2.mp4?t=1771085065\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >沉浸于一个完全手绘的世界，其艺术灵感源自吉卜力工作室。游戏的视觉风格唤起一种奇妙而宁静的氛围，类似于《风之旅人》和《Gris》等作品。每个场景都精心打造，旨在创造出美丽、动人且纯粹的体验。</p>",
